title: Ep 25: I Took A Pill in Ibiza (pt 2)
itunes:title: Ep 25: I Took A Pill in Ibiza (pt 2)
description: Did you actually think we weren’t going to use that for an episode title? Shannon and Marissa leave for Ibiza to get as rowdy as possible. Mission accomplished… or was it? Also wtf is a come-up? After quite the Ibiza club experience, another run in with a mouse, and lots of.. corn (?) the girls have to make a decision whether to go on to Seville as originally planned or head back to Barcelona to continue Shan’s fairytale. Will Shannon cross paths with Barcelona man again? Find out that and more in Episode 12!
